OL,7,FSean 'Diddy' Combs has been denied
OL,8,Fbail a second time, with the judge
OL,9,Fsaying the prosecution had proved "by
OL,10,Fclear and convincing evidence" that
OL,11,Fnothing could guarantee the hip-hop
OL,12,Fmogul won't tamper with witnesses.
OL,14,FUS District Judge Andrew L. Carter
OL,15,Fhanded down the ruling after
OL,16,Fprosecutors and defence lawyers
OL,17,Fpresented strenuous arguments for and
OL,18,Fagainst a $50 million (#37.85m) bail
OL,19,Fpackage.
